# Windsurf — UI design only

Apply **only** when designing, styling, or building visual UI.

## Activation

- User requests design system, styling, or layout/visual changes
- Files: `_sass/**`, `_includes/**`, `_layouts/**`, `assets/css/**`, `index.html`, `design/**`

## Do not apply

Config, content-only, analytics, or non-visual paths.

## Source of truth

`design/design-system.md` — Organic / Natural (wabi-sabi).

## Stack

Jekyll + SCSS + HTML includes. Tokens → `_sass/` variables; preserve skin/partial structure.

## Constraints

Earth palette, Fraunces/Nunito, soft tinted shadows, grain texture, organic blob radii, pill components, glass nav pill, blob backgrounds, gentle 300–500ms transitions, section `py-32` + varied max-widths. See design doc for buttons, cards, inputs, layout, responsive, and accessibility.
